    <h2><font color="#000080"><!-- 2004-08-31 -->
    
    Annotating Peano Numbers
    
    </font></h2>
    
    
    <p>
	<h3>Annotating Peano Numbers</h3>This is a new blog created specifically for a collaborative-articulation project.&nbsp; The idea is to develop an understanding of abstraction, syntax, semantics, and meaning of programming-language interfaces.&nbsp; We will undertake that using a concrete manifestation of Peano Numbers.&nbsp; This will also be revealing about the application of mathematical abstractions in connection with engineered artifacts -- computers and programs -- and their behavior.<br /><br />This post is simply to prime the pump and ensure that everything is working properly.
    </p>
